OL,3,CMan and woman killed in crash between
OL,4,Ccar and lorry
OL,6,FPolice are appealing for witnesses
OL,7,Fafter two people died following a
OL,8,Fcrash between a car and a lorry.
OL,10,FEmergency services were called to
OL,11,FGisburn Road in Sawley in Lancashire,
OL,12,Fat 3.44pm on Saturday 11 April.
OL,14,FIt followed reports of a collision
OL,15,Fbetween a green Mazda MX5, travelling
OL,16,Fwestbound towards Clitheroe from
OL,17,FGisburn, and a DAF HGV travelling in
OL,18,Fthe opposite direction.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
