PN,39802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776096667
OL,3,CMan and woman killed in crash between
OL,4,Ccar and lorry
OL,6,FThe driver of the Mazda car, a 49-year-
OL,7,Fold man and the passenger, a 25-year-
OL,8,Fold woman, were pronounced dead at the
OL,9,Fscene.
OL,11,FThe HGV driver was unhurt. Lancashire
OL,12,FPolice say he stopped at the scene.
OL,14,FSgt Paul McCurrie, of Lancashire
OL,15,FPolice Roads Policing Team said: "Very
OL,16,Fsadly, a man and a woman have died in
OL,17,Fthis collision, and primarily, my and
OL,18,Fmy team's thoughts are with all those
OL,19,Fwho knew and loved them at this time.
OL,26,@wD@bOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776096667
OL,3,CMan and woman killed in crash between
OL,4,Ccar and lorry
OL,6,F"Enquiries into how the collision
OL,7,Foccurred are ongoing, and as part of
OL,8,Fthose enquiries, I need to ask for
OL,9,Fyour help.
OL,11,F"If you witnessed the collision, or
OL,12,Fhave any footage that could assist our
OL,13,Fenquiries, we would be really keen to
OL,14,Fspeak to you.
OL,16,F"I'm appealing to you directly to ask
OL,17,Fthat if you were driving on the A59
OL,18,Fprior to the collision in this area,
OL,19,Fand have a dashcam, to please check
OL,20,Fyour footage. If you have captured the
OL,21,FMazda, or the HGV, please let us know.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
